Source: helix
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Helix Team <anemoi_ai@proton.me>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cmake (>= 3.22), ninja-build
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/anemoi-ai/helix
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: libhelix1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenAI-isomorphic on-device LLM library (runtime)
 Helix is an embeddable C/C++ shared library that exposes a single-header
 OpenAI Chat Completions API backed by llama.cpp.  No subprocess, no open
 ports, no network calls.
 .
 This package contains the shared library required at runtime.

Package: libhelix-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: libhelix1 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenAI-isomorphic on-device LLM library (development files)
 Helix is an embeddable C/C++ shared library that exposes a single-header
 OpenAI Chat Completions API backed by llama.cpp.
 .
 This package contains the header, pkg-config file, and CMake config needed
 to build software that links against libhelix.

Package: helix-tools
Architecture: any
Section: utils
Depends: libhelix1 (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenAI-isomorphic on-device LLM library (tools)
 This package contains helix-doctor (diagnostic tool) and helix-bench
 (benchmark harness).
